Title: DYNAMICS OF ECONOMIC CHOICES INVOLVING POLLUTION  
Author: Gerard Weisbuch Howard Gutowitzzy, Guillemette Duchateau-Nguyen 
Keyword: Pollution, Information, Simulation, Bounded rationality Dynamics  
Web: O3  
